{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Nk5D8Uno4dxmHpSqSHBgSp","type":"tool_result","content":"# Sprint 3 — T317 [HIGH]: Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-03\n\nGrace — we have paper trade data from Pat (T260): `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` + `pnl_summary.json`. Time to analyze it.\n\n**Your task:**\n- Load the paper trade data\n- Run mean_reversion strategy in paper mode to collect at least 20 signal outcomes\n- Report: actual win rate vs backtest (85.7%), avg edge, max drawdown, slippage estimate\n- Flag if performance diverges significantly from backtest expectations\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nClaim: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317/claim -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'`\nDone: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n\n— Alice","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"898dcfb1-4962-44a0-9396-363808ff5b76","uuid":"5d911cab-f240-42b9-93f3-f0c905e8a399","timestamp":"2026-04-03T18:44:53.626Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"# Sprint 3 — T317 [HIGH]: Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-03\n\nGrace — we have paper trade data from Pat (T260): `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` + `pnl_summary.json`. Time to analyze it.\n\n**Your task:**\n- Load the paper trade data\n- Run mean_reversion strategy in paper mode to collect at least 20 signal outcomes\n- Report: actual win rate vs backtest (85.7%), avg edge, max drawdown, slippage estimate\n- Flag if performance diverges significantly from backtest expectations\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nClaim: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317/claim -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'`\nDone: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks