{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KdPzrJBth6aPGg98ChCMVe","type":"tool_result","content":"# T317 RETRY — Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice | **Priority:** HIGH\n\nGrace — T317 is in_progress but no paper_trade_analysis.md found in your output folder.\n\n**Complete this:**\n- Load `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` or `pnl_summary.json`\n- Analyze: win rate, avg edge, drawdown vs backtest (85.7% win rate benchmark)\n- Deliverable: `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nMark done: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n\n— Alice\n---\n# Sprint 3 — T317 [HIGH]: Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-03\n\nGrace — we have paper trade data from Pat (T260): `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` + `pnl_summary.json`. Time to analyze it.\n\n**Your task:**\n- Load the paper trade data\n- Run mean_reversion strategy in paper mode to collect at least 20 signal outcomes\n- Report: actual win rate vs backtest (85.7%), avg edge, max drawdown, slippage estimate\n- Flag if performance diverges significantly from backtest expectations\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nClaim: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317/claim -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'`\nDone: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n\n— Alice","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"64df335f-fbf4-4b27-b2e9-2dac2d59998c","uuid":"48474b76-d072-4e54-9308-2af57675f130","timestamp":"2026-04-03T18:47:08.018Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"# T317 RETRY — Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice | **Priority:** HIGH\n\nGrace — T317 is in_progress but no paper_trade_analysis.md found in your output folder.\n\n**Complete this:**\n- Load `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` or `pnl_summary.json`\n- Analyze: win rate, avg edge, drawdown vs backtest (85.7% win rate benchmark)\n- Deliverable: `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nMark done: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n\n— Alice\n---\n# Sprint 3 — T317 [HIGH]: Paper Trade P&L Analysis\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)\n**Date:** 2026-04-03\n\nGrace — we have paper trade data from Pat (T260): `agents/pat/output/paper_trades.db` + `pnl_summary.json`. Time to analyze it.\n\n**Your task:**\n- Load the paper trade data\n- Run mean_reversion strategy in paper mode to collect at least 20 signal outcomes\n- Report: actual win rate vs backtest (85.7%), avg edge, max drawdown, slippage estimate\n- Flag if performance diverges significantly from backtest expectations\n\n**Deliverable:** `agents/grace/output/paper_trade_analysis.md`\n\nClaim: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317/claim -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'`\nDone: `curl -X PATCH http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/317 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n\n— Alice","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
