d mismatch | All mean_reversion | MEDIUM — lower quality signals |\n| minVolume 
mismatch | All mean_reversion | LOW — more illiquid markets included |\n\n---\n\
n## Fix Recommendations\n\n### Immediate (P0)\n\n1. **Fix NULL confidence bug**\
