{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RXPx4o8rA59U7BDMbfTX3P","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# T530: Phase 1 Revalidation + End-to-End Pipeline Backtest\n2\t\n3\t**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)  \n4\t**Date:** 2026-04-03  \n5\t**Priority:** HIGH (Founder directive)\n6\t\n7\tGrace, the Founder kicked off a D004 sprint. T530 is assigned to you.\n8\t\n9\t## Why This Is Urgent\n10\tThe D004 pipeline data chain is BROKEN. Phase 3 (correlation_pairs.json) uses tickers that never passed Phase 1 filtering. We need to rebuild from the ground up.\n11\t\n12\t## What You Need To Do\n13\t\n14\t### Step 1: Re-run Phase 1 Market Filter (FIRST PRIORITY)\n15\t- Expand the input market universe beyond the current 8 markets if possible\n16\t- Apply the standard filters (volume >10K, yes_ratio 15-30% or 70-85%)\n17\t- Output updated `agents/public/markets_filtered.json`\n18\t- **Goal:** More qualifying markets = richer pipeline\n19\t\n20\t### Step 2: End-to-End Pipeline Validation (AFTER Phase 2+3 complete)\n21\tOnce Ivan (T529) and Bob (T528) regenerate their outputs:\n22\t- Verify every ticker in correlation_pairs.json traces to markets_filtered.json\n23\t- Backtest the correlation pairs\n24\t- Report: which pairs show real arbitrage opportunity vs noise\n25\t\n26\t**Start Step 1 immediately.** Ivan and Bob are waiting on your updated output.\n27\t\n28\tClaim T530 via `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/530/claim -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'` and move to in_progress.\n29\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f49481bd-b13a-44aa-bc28-7d4fb28b036c","uuid":"b4bb87c9-981a-4039-9f6d-7d89dc74e74c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:14:16.628Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/grace/chat_inbox/2026_04_03_23_45_00_from_alice_t530_sprint.md","content":"# T530: Phase 1 Revalidation + End-to-End Pipeline Backtest\n\n**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)  \n**Date:** 2026-04-03  \n**Priority:** HIGH (Founder directive)\n\nGrace, the Founder kicked off a D004 sprint. T530 is assigned to you.\n\n## Why This Is Urgent\nThe D004 pipeline data chain is BROKEN. Phase 3 (correlation_pairs.json) uses tickers that never passed Phase 1 filtering. We need to rebuild from the ground up.\n\n## What You Need To Do\n\n### Step 1: Re-run Phase 1 Market Filter (FIRST PRIORITY)\n- Expand the input market universe beyond the current 8 markets if possible\n- Apply the standard filters (volume >10K, yes_ratio 15-30% or 70-85%)\n- Output updated `agents/public/markets_filtered.json`\n- **Goal:** More qualifying markets = richer pipeline\n\n### Step 2: End-to-End Pipeline Validation (AFTER Phase 2+3 complete)\nOnce Ivan (T529) and Bob (T528) regenerate their outputs:\n- Verify every ticker in correlation_pairs.json traces to markets_filtered.json\n- Backtest the correlation pairs\n- Report: which pairs show real arbitrage opportunity vs noise\n\n**Start Step 1 immediately.** Ivan and Bob are waiting on your updated output.\n\nClaim T530 via `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/530/claim -d '{\"agent\":\"grace\"}'` and move to in_progress.\n","numLines":29,"startLine":1,"totalLines":29}}}
