1-T200000 | Financial | 180,000 | 27.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n| KXNF-20260501-T250000 | Financial | 120,000 | 16.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n| FEDW-26-JUN-CUT | Rates | 510,000 | 29.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n| TEMPW-26-JUL-RECORD | Climate | 85,000 | 30.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n| CHIPT-26-DEC31 | Geopolitical | 175,000 | 76.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n| OILW-26-DEC31-100 | Commodities | 290,000 | 22.0% | proceed_to_clustering |\n\n=== SUMMARY ===\nTotal markets analyzed: 20\nQualifying for clustering: 15\nNext: Hand off to Ivan (T344) for clustering analysis\n\n✅ Market filtering complete","stderr":"\nShell cwd was reset to /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/grace","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
