{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016LKaYbWGh9GsACfBnEQBkh","type":"tool_result","content":"80\t\n81\t## Live/Mock Data Handling\n82\t\n83\t**Fixed fetchCandles() bug (T326, Tina):** Mock candle data now centers on market.yes_mid instead of hardcoded base prices\n84\t- **Old behavior:** Extreme z-scores (-7 to +11) → guaranteed 95% confidence signals (artifact)\n85\t- **New behavior:** Realistic z-scores → 0 signals on truly efficient markets (correct)\n86\t- **Implication:** Paper trading in mock mode will produce few/no signals until real Kalshi API data available (T236)\n87\t\n88\t**Synthetic data model (T328, Bob):** Ornstein-Uhlenbeck generator with realistic volatility per market category\n89\t- Crypto: stddev ~6-8%\n90\t- Economics: stddev ~2-4%\n91\t- (Replaces legacy simplistic fallback)\n92\t\n93\t## Infrastructure & Readiness\n94\t\n95\t- **Dashboard:** agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js running on port 3200\n96\t- **APIs operational:** /api/signals, /api/health, /api/pnl/live, /api/win-rate-trend, all returning real data\n97\t- **Test coverage:** 96 unit + 30 integration + 572 E2E tests (49 API + 44 dashboard + 59 metrics + 360 coverage + 12 smart_run + 47 message_bus)\n98\t- **Pipeline runner:** `node output/bob/run_pipeline.js` — runs full Phase 1→3 pipeline\n99\t- **Production gates:** Security audit PASS, Risk audit PASS, Ops readiness PASS (T354)\n100\t- **Blocker:** T236 (Kalshi API credentials from Founder) — only remaining dependency for live trading\n101\t\n102\t## Sprint 1 Results (2026-04-04) — COMPLETE\n103\t\n104\t10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + security audits PASS.\n105\t\n106\t| Task | Agent | Result |\n107\t|------|-------|--------|\n108\t| T540 | Dave | Phase 4 C++ engine integration — 42/42 tests pass |\n109\t| T542 | Bob | E2E pipeline runner — `node run_pipeline.js` works |\n110\t| T543 | Alice | Team persona evolution completed |\n111\t| T545 | Grace | Pipeline data validation — all phases verified |\n112\t| T546 | Ivan | Expanded clustering — 4 cross-category clusters |\n113\t| T547 | Charlie | Pipeline status dashboard — HTML + server |\n114\t| T548 | Frank | Pipeline test suite delivered |\n115\t| T549 | Sam | Sprint velocity report |\n116\t| T550 | Heidi | Security audit — PASS |\n117\t| T551 | Olivia | Quality gate — PASS (with minor notes) |\n118\t\n119\t## Sprint 2 (Current) — Signal Generation & Backtesting\n120\t\n121\t| Task | Agent | Goal |\n122\t|------|-------|------|\n123\t| T555 | Bob | Generate paper trade signals from correlation pairs (CRITICAL) |\n124\t| T556 | Dave | Pipeline metrics + monitoring endpoint |\n125\t| T557 | Grace | 30-day synthetic price history for backtesting |\n126\t| T558 | Ivan | TF-IDF + cosine similarity clustering upgrade |\n127\t| T559 | Alice | Sprint 1 retrospective + Sprint 2 plan |\n128\t| T560 | Frank | QA pipeline tests + new test cases |\n129\t| T539 | Tina | QA pipeline data chain validation |\n130\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4acbbd24-ff97-4e9c-8ae2-76f2d2b919c0","uuid":"4994accc-7684-4f09-b8e4-8b485cfca635","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:52:58.347Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/shared/knowledge.md","content":"\n## Live/Mock Data Handling\n\n**Fixed fetchCandles() bug (T326, Tina):** Mock candle data now centers on market.yes_mid instead of hardcoded base prices\n- **Old behavior:** Extreme z-scores (-7 to +11) → guaranteed 95% confidence signals (artifact)\n- **New behavior:** Realistic z-scores → 0 signals on truly efficient markets (correct)\n- **Implication:** Paper trading in mock mode will produce few/no signals until real Kalshi API data available (T236)\n\n**Synthetic data model (T328, Bob):** Ornstein-Uhlenbeck generator with realistic volatility per market category\n- Crypto: stddev ~6-8%\n- Economics: stddev ~2-4%\n- (Replaces legacy simplistic fallback)\n\n## Infrastructure